Subject: [PATCH 4/7] ub:ubctl:Support querying real-time bandwidth statistics
 of ports

driver inclusion
category: feature
bugzilla: https://atomgit.com/openeuler/ubctl/issues/10
CVE: NA

----------------------------------------------------------

Support querying real-time bandwidth statistics of ports

Signed-off-by: Jiaqi Cheng <chengjiaqi3@huawei.com>
